Feature: Paint Application Launch and Basic Operations
    As a user
    I want to launch Microsoft Paint application
    So that I can verify it opens correctly and is ready to use

    @smoke @critical
    Scenario: Launch Paint application successfully
        Given I have Paint application available
        When I launch the Paint application
        Then Paint application should open successfully
        And the window title should contain "Paint"

    @smoke
    Scenario: Verify Paint canvas is visible after launch
        Given I have Paint application available
        When I launch the Paint application
        Then the Paint canvas should be visible

    @ui
    Scenario: Maximize Paint window
        Given I have launched Paint application
        When I maximize the Paint window
        Then the Paint window should be in maximized state

    @ui
    Scenario Outline: Change window state
        Given I have launched Paint application
        When I change the window state to "<state>"
        Then the Paint window should be in "<state>" state

        Examples:
        | state     |
        | Maximized |
        | Normal    |